<div class="intro-header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <div class="intro-message">
          <%= image_tag('ucalgary-logo.jpg', height: '200') %>
          <h1>The First PHAS Symposium</h1>
          <h3>November 12, 2015</h3>
          <hr class="intro-divder"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="instructions">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
        <p>
          It is a pleasure to invite you to the First PHAS Symposium. The conference is organized by the PHAS graduate students and postdoctoral research fellows and will take place at the main campus, in SB 142 and SB 148, of the University of Calgary on November 12, 2015.
        </p>
        <p>
          The purpose of the PHAS Symposium is to bring graduate students and postdoctoral research fellows from various research areas and groups together. All PHAS gradate students and postdoctoral research fellows are welcome and encouraged to submit an abstract for an oral and/or a poster presentation. There is no registration fee. Furthermore, refreshment and lunch will be provided.
        </p>

        <p>
          Abstract submissionÂ is now open and the deadline is October 25, 2015. To submit your abstract, please fill out the form below. 
        </p>

        <p>
          We are looking forward to see you all in the First PHAS Symposium. 
        </p>

        <p>
          Sincerely,
          </p>

          <p>
          <br/>
          The Organizing Committee (order alphabetically):
          <br/>
          Jonathan Johannes
          <br/>
          Behzad Khanaliloo
          <br/>
          Farokh Mivehvar
          <br/>
          Anna Ordog
          <br/>
          Lucile Veissier
          <br/>
          Elizabeth Watt
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<hr/>

<% flash.each do |name, msg| %>
  <%= content_tag :div, msg, class: (name == 'success' ? "bg-success" : "bg-danger") %>
<% end %>

<div class="content-section-a">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <%= form_for :submission, url: submissions_path, html: {class: 'form-horizontal'} do |f| %>
        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :presentation_type, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label required' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <label class="checkbox-inline">
              <%= f.radio_button(:presentation_type, "oral", checked: true) %>
              oral
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox-inline">
              <%= f.radio_button(:presentation_type, "poster") %>
              poster
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox-inline">
              <%= f.radio_button(:presentation_type, "attender") %>
              attender
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :name, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label required' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <%= f.text_field :name, class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'Name' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :email, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label required' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <%= f.text_field :email, class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'Email' %>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :attender_type, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label required' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <label class="checkbox-inline">
              <%= f.radio_button(:attender_type, "msc", checked: true) %>
              MSc 
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox-inline">
              <%= f.radio_button(:attender_type, "phd") %>
              PhD 
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox-inline">
              <%= f.radio_button(:attender_type, "postdoc") %>
              Postdoctoral Fellow 
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :sub_department, 'Group', class: 'col-sm-2 control-label required togglable' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <%= f.text_field :sub_department, class: 'form-control togglable', placeholder: 'Group (ex: Quantum)' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :title, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label required togglable' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <%= f.text_field :title, class: 'form-control togglable', placeholder: 'Title (200 character limit)' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :abstract, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label required togglable' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <%= f.text_area :abstract, class: 'form-control togglable', placeholder: 'Abstract (1000 character limit)' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr/>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :dietary_restrictions, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <%= f.text_area :dietary_restrictions, class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'Dietary restrictions' %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= f.label :will_attend_social_event, class: 'col-sm-2 control-label' %>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <%= f.check_box :will_attend_social_event, {}, true, false %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='form-group'>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
            <%= f.submit 'Submit', class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr/>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <p>Please contact <%= link_to "jonny.p.johannes@ucalgary.ca", "mailto:jonny.p.johannes@ucalgary.ca" %> if you have any questions about the form.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
  $(document).ready(function(){
    submission.init();
  });
</script>
